msgid "{ios} app"
msgstr "{ios} programa"

#. Body copy for the iOS app card on the download page. Preserve {premium_tier_name} exactly; make clear the iOS app is in a limited TestFlight beta with capped slots and that a public release is coming. Do not promise that subscribing grants beta access. Preserve placeholders exactly.
#: fluxer_marketing/generated:platform_support.mobile.ios.body
msgctxt "platform_support.mobile.ios.body"
msgid ""
"As of 15 June 2026, the {ios} app is in a limited {testflight} beta with a small group of {premium_tier_name} subscribers. {testflight} slots are limited, so the best way in for most people is to wait for the public release."
msgstr ""
"Nuo 2026 m. birželio 15 d. {ios} programa yra riboto {testflight} beta versijoje su maža „{premium_tier_name}“ prenumeratorių grupe. {testflight} vietų yra ribotai, todėl daugumai žmonių geriausias būdas yra laukti viešo leidimo."

